Koga Shuko/Unitron/Hades/Anubis:



Unitron leapt in the air, transforming into a space fighter, zooming thorugh 
the sky, the rocket missing him.


---

Key laughs as shots dig into his heavily armored hide.  Turning, he pulled a 
missile launcher, firing a rocket at Key's torso.

---

Hades slams to the ground from the combs of attacks.

---

Anubis laughs, not being shot out.  Raising his missile launcher, he fired a 
rocket at Blue Stinger, five plasma blasts from his rifle at Antagony's lower 
torso.
